<plot>A rainy night in southern California. Heather is a new counselor at a teen crisis hotline, 1-888-talk-2-us. Jennifer, a college student who may be using drugs and is definitely in crisis, tries to phone her father to ask for money. Cliff, a car salesman, starts a conversation with a stranger in a bar. Robert sees Jennifer shoplifting and thinks of the daughter he recently lost. Alexi, a seasoned counselor, talks to Heather during a power outage. The people circle and connect; communications misfire. Is there a chance of sunshine?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?492040</url></doc>
